coh_definition_description: This is intended to capture patients who have been diagnosed with hypertension for the first time.
coh_development_process: A compilation of various hypertension diagnosis codes were developed and peer-reviewed by a cardiologist
coh_valid_proc_desc: We randomly sampled 100 patients for a manual chart review. Ties were resolved by majority vote of 3 experts.
coh_valid_data_desc: We used a claims database with approximately 200k records
